  "issue_number": 4298,
  "issue_title": "\ud83c\udfa8 Style: Add `is`/`has`/`can` prefix to unexported boolean struct fields",
  "issue_body": "Per Go naming conventions, unexported boolean fields should use `is`/`has`/`can`/`should` prefix so they read as true/false questions. Found ~24 violations across internal (unexported) fields:\n\n| File | Current | Suggested |\n|---|---|---|\n| `app.go:111` | `routesRefreshed` | `hasRoutesRefreshed` |\n| `ctx.go:74` | `matched` | `isMatched` |\n| `ctx.go:75` | `skipNonUseRoutes` | `shouldSkipNonUseRoutes` |\n| `group.go:20` | `anyRouteDefined` | `hasAnyRoute` |\n| `bind.go:42` | `dontHandleErrs` | `shouldSkipErrHandling` |\n| `bind.go:43` | `skipValidation` | `shouldSkipValidation` |\n| `client/request.go:72` | `disablePathNormalizing` | `isPathNormalizingDisabled` |\n| `client/client.go:67` | `debug` | `isDebug` |\n| `client/client.go:68` | `disablePathNormalizing` | `isPathNormalizingDisabled` |\n| `client/cookiejar.go:53,58` | `hostOnly` | `isHostOnly` |\n| `client/cookiejar.go:59` | `ok` | `isOk` |\n| `log/default.go:29` | `ok` | `isOk` |\n| `domain.go:34` | `matched` | `isMatched` |\n| `middleware/session/session.go:25` | `fresh` | `isFresh` |\n| `middleware/session/middleware.go:21` | `destroyed` | `isDestroyed` |\n| `middleware/sse/sse.go:91` | `closed` | `isClosed` |\n| `middleware/cache/manager.go:51` | `redactKeys` | `shouldRedactKeys` |\n| `middleware/limiter/manager.go:27` | `redactKeys` | `shouldRedactKeys` |\n| `middleware/csrf/storage_manager.go:26` | `redactKeys` | `shouldRedactKeys` |\n| `middleware/logger/config.go:98` | `enableColors` | `areColorsEnabled` |\n| `middleware/logger/config.go:99` | `enableLatency` | `isLatencyEnabled` |\n\nAll are unexported \u2014 no public API breakage. Purely cosmetic, but improves readability.",
  "merged_at": "2026-05-21T11:58:41Z",
